name: react-bootstrap-table2-paginator
description: it's the pagination addon for react-bootstrap-table2

scripts.build: babel src --out-dir dist --extensions '.js,.jsx' --presets '@babel/preset-env,@babel/preset-react' && cp ./style/react-bootstrap-table2-paginator.scss ./dist && node-sass dist/react-bootstrap-table2-paginator.scss > dist/react-bootstrap-table2-paginator.css  && cleancss dist/react-bootstrap-table2-paginator.css -o dist/react-bootstrap-table2-paginator.min.css

author: AllenFang
